    <summary>Generate informative test pattern wallpapers for every display from a TOML config file or CLI flags.</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
## BgRaster

A fast, single-file console application that generates per-output wallpapers
and assigns them directly to every display using the Windows `IDesktopWallpaper` COM interface.

### Features

- Per-output wallpaper rendering with independent configuration per display
- Crosshair, grid, circle, labeled edges, logo, and text layers
- TOML configuration with CLI overrides
- ASUS ProArt color space support
- No runtime dependencies — a single AOT-compiled executable

### Quick start

```powershell
BgRaster --text "Hello World" --grid-size 64 --circle-size 200
```
    ]]></description>
